---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="404 - dns.js.gripe"
  description="The requested dns.js.gripe page was not found."
  canonical="https://dns.js.gripe/404.html"
  alternates={[
    { lang: "zh-CN", href: "https://dns.js.gripe/404.html" },
    { lang: "en", href: "https://dns.js.gripe/404.html" }
  ]}
>
  <main class="shell help-shell" id="main">
    <article class="help-page">
      <header class="help-hero">
        <img src="/media/favicon.png" alt="" />
        <div>
          <p>404</p>
          <h1>页面不存在</h1>
        </div>
      </header>
      <section>
        <h2>找不到这个页面</h2>
        <p>这个地址没有可访问的页面。你可以返回首页继续查询 DNS。</p>
      </section>
      <section>
        <h2>Page not found</h2>
        <p>This address does not have a public page. Return home to continue querying DNS.</p>
      </section>
    </article>
    <footer class="page-footer">
      <div>
        <a href="/">首页</a>
        <a href="/en/">Home</a>
      </div>
    </footer>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
